        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ben2 Eagle builds upon the standard Ben2 architecture with enhanced attention mechanisms and optimized inference kernels. It supports a context window of up to 8,192 tokens and is fine-tuned for conversational and completion tasks. Key improvements include reduced latency and higher throughput, making it ideal for real-time API applications."
