            "type": "text",
            "text": "When deploying ben 2 eagle in production, consider using container orchestration tools like Kubernetes for scalability. Monitor key metrics such as inference latency, error rates, and memory usage. Implement health checks and auto-scaling policies to handle traffic spikes. Additionally, use load balancers to distribute requests evenly across instances."
