            "text": "Fine-tune Ben2 Eagle by adjusting parameters like temperature and top_p based on your use case. Employ caching for frequent requests to reduce load on the model. Batch processing can improve throughput for non-real-time tasks. Regularly profile your API to identify bottlenecks and optimize accordingly."
